Subject: perf annotate-data: Add a cache for global variable types
Git-commit: 55ee3d005d62279d3951a26d5c211a4d9aebc222
Patch-mainline: v6.10-rc1
References: perf-sp7-v6.11-userspace-update

They are often searched by many different places.  Let's add a cache
for them to reduce the duplicate DWARF access.

